33 in the annual earning limit shall be rounded to the next
34 lowest multiple of one thousand dollars ($1,000) with any
35 amount in excess of the one thousand dollar ($1,000) multiple
36 considered in determining the increase for the following year.
37 Each adjustment shall be based on the increase in the index
